I modified my box 50 with the current circuit and it works !  I love  this 
new board.  

I wanted a box that sounded exactly like Chris Moons little blue box and  
now i have two that sound like it.  I e-mailed Chris, he also agreed.  

The way they talk is so unique, it&#39;s made in the white noise.  I  hardly 
can make out any radio in it at all, only spirit communication.   This is what 
i&#39;ve been working for.

It&#39;s so reliable too with only a few seconds of warm up time.  Got it  
running on 6V

-Steve H.




